A short recoil cam roller lock barrel allows higher pressure ammunition. Ammo is readily available and cheap. This weapon was originally designed for 9mm. The result is a very powerful pistol with a roller lockup and a milled upper and lower. It's known to shoot through balistic vests. Why so cheap?
